prediction.sparql:
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?team ?label WHERE {
  fb:m.05cb70 fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?roster .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team ?team .
  ?team rdfs:label ?label .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.from ?from .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.to ?to .
  FILTER ( ?from <= '2011' && ( ?to >= '2011' || ?to = '' ) )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?team ?teamName WHERE {
  fb:m.03rsd2 fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?roster .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team ?team .
  ?team rdfs:label ?teamName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?teamName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?religion ?percentage ?date WHERE {
  fb:m.09c7w0 fb:location.statistical_region.religions ?religionPercentage .
  ?religionPercentage fb:location.religion_percentage.religion ?religion .
  ?religionPercentage fb:location.religion_percentage.percentage ?percentage .
  ?religionPercentage fb:location.religion_percentage.date ?date .
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT ?state WHERE {
  fb:m.02mjmr fb:people.person.place_of_birth ?placeOfBirth .
  ?placeOfBirth fb:location.location.containedby ?state .
  ?state rdf:type fb:location.us_state .
}

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?finals ?year WHERE {
  fb:m.0j6tr fb:sports.sports_team_participation.sport_event ?event .
  ?event rdf:type fb:sports.sports_league_championship .
  ?event fb:time.event.year ?year .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?year )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?team ?teamLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0dr5g9 fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?team .
  ?team rdfs:label ?teamLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?teamLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?containedByLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0g5r_z_ fb:location.location.containedby ?containedBy .
  ?containedBy rdfs:label ?containedByLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?containedByLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?degree ?institution ?year WHERE {
  fb:m.0271_s fb:people.person.education ?education .
  ?education fb:education.education.degree ?degree .
  ?education fb:education.education.institution ?institution .
  ?education fb:education.education.end_date ?year .
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?superbowl ?label WHERE {
  fb:m.070xg fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?superbowl .
  ?superbowl rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?award ?forWork WHERE {
  fb:m.0fb1q fb:award.award_winner.awards_won ?award .
  ?award fb:award.award_for ?forWork .
  ?award fb:award.award_category ?category .
  ?category fb:award.award_category.category_for ?awardType .
  FILTER ( ?awardType = 'Grammy' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?continent ?latitude ?longitude WHERE {
  fb:m.0169t fb:base.locations.countries.continent ?continent .
  fb:m.0169t fb:location.location.geolocation ?geolocation .
  ?geolocation fb:location.geocode.latitude ?latitude .
  ?geolocation fb:location.geocode.longitude ?longitude .
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?governor WHERE {
  fb:m.02xry fb:government.governmental_jurisdiction.governing_officials ?governor .
  ?governor fb:government.government_position_held.office_position_or_title fb:m.01h_0k .
  ?governor fb:government.government_position_held.from ?startDate .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?startDate )
LIMIT 1
